summary: An Ordinance appropriating money the sum of One Hundred Forty-nine and 97/100 ($149.97) Dollars our of the General Fund of The City of Seattle to pay the claim of Island Transportation Company for damages to Steamer "Camano" caused by Fireboat "Duwamish" colliding with said Steamer on the 14th day of January, 1914, (File No. 55343), and authorizing the drawing of a warrant therefor.
